	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hmm... I don't have either of these problems. I have posts as old as three years still showing the images correctly. I do get 'read more' links, but that's intentional; I use the &lt;!--more--&gt; tags. Do you include an excerpt in each article? If so, maybe try removing the excerpt and seeing if it then shows the entire article. I wonder if it could also be the theme you're using doing things a little weird (assuming you're not using the default theme).

		

